CHAPTER XXXIV

RECAPTURE OF PRZEMYSL


The counteroffensive ended       of necessity       on May 24,
1915. The Russians could still offer an effective resistance between
Krukienice and Mosciska, but the pressure of continuous attack against
their positions around Hussakow grew fiercer every hour. The enemy
